        <h3><i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i> The Problem</h3>
        <p>
          In India, finding a clean and accessible public toilet can be a real challenge.
          Many struggle not only to locate restrooms, but also to know about their cleanliness,
          safety, accessibility, and whether they are paid or free.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> Our Solution</h3>
        <p>
          <strong>Where Is My Loo?</strong> is a crowd-sourced platform designed to solve this everyday problem:
        </p>
        <ul>
